commit.message:
mips.c (function_arg): Don't pass NULL_TREE to host_integerp.

2001-01-02  Jeffrey Oldham  <oldham@codesourcery.com>

	* config/mips/mips.c (function_arg): Don't pass NULL_TREE to
	host_integerp.

From-SVN: r38627
